HISAT PIPELINE

1.	Converting GFF file to GTF 
a.	Using gffread package 
b.	Input: GFF
c.	Output: GTF

2.	Hisat2 extract Splice Site script called “hisat2_splice_site.sh”
a.	Using extract_splice_site.py 
b.	Input: GTF file 
c.	Output: splice sites   “file.ss”


3.	Hisat2 extract exon script called “hisat2_exon.sh”
a.	Using extract_exon.py
b.	Input: GTF file 
c.	Output: exons  “file.exon”

4.	Hisat2 build index script 
a.	Inputs: 
i.	IN_SS (splice sites file)
ii.	IN_EX (exon file)
iii.	IN_FA (genome fasta file)
b.	Output: hisat2 indices

5. hisat2 alignment script
Inputs
  a. Path To Directory of trimed fastq files containing R1s and R2s                                                                                                                                                                           
  b. Path To Output Directory to store sam files outputed from this script                                                                                                                                                                    
  c. Path To Index file (indexing based name)                                                                                                                                                                                                 
  d. Path To Annotation file                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  e. Path To splice sites file
Output
  a. sam files
